        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Evacuees Tax Relief Act of 2005 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow individual taxpayers to elect either a tax credit or tax deduction for up to $5,000 of their voluntary or mandatory evacuation expenses due to a disaster.</p>]]></text>
